    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "f4fa9e74-a5c9-4d86-ba72-68201f1a64ec",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "131a33f3-c29e-4f49-8854-b91c1e5a33be",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "6afb5c74-1a63-46c4-be30-30033ef9020d",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we'll be doing a demonstration and a series of experiments on incendiary and explosive devices.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeInventory",
                    "id": "cc5c1360-4b20-4708-ab78-654f68b20231",
                    "propId": "f9b2d9af-2da3-4f57-bb7d-00c83690c74c",
                    "sceneId": "a2508b7e-a177-4a96-93bd-4d8ab88dffc4",
                    "change": "1",
                    "count": 1,
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0e7016e5-7770-417e-b525-65439d26cc8a",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We will start by constructing a Boom. A Boom is a booby-trap device that, once triggered, will explode when something touches it. ",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "a30c2e56-6544-4c34-88fd-f0bbc669c936",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "While I will be supplying the chemicals for this experiment, if you have fulfilled your homework assignments by gathering the components of Charcoal, Sulphur, and Phosphorus, you'll be able to replicate previous experiments.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "eb52e762-8303-415c-95a2-c18d112525af",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before we get started?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "8418d5f1-6255-4e95-add3-1641e710708e",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "0a91bbe1-6432-47f9-a8d4-58cf1f46c355",
                            "text": "Talk About the Joy of Explosives",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "1506ddf1-8f8f-4d46-8916-4b3d0b1ad43e",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "32",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "2dd26192-a923-43a0-bf52-e5e145225776",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f338acda-c10c-4da0-a268-2f62541e767e",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "So we'll be devoting this entire class to blowing things up? And here people think science is boring!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3676f0f3-41da-424f-b535-e9cb0783e337",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "People think Science is boring? How could anyone consider uncovering the very building blocks of the universe to be boring?",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ee28b7ca-b9cb-418f-8937-b58c593a22fc",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "No, Shawn, Science is never boring. People are boring. People are prejudicial, narrow-minded, ignoramuses who wouldn't know metamorphic from metaphysical!",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1c749620-cb6b-4df1-bbd8-04bb0a94fc7d",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Science is a rational approach to viewing reality. Unless, of course, you are dealing with irrational numbers, but that's more geometry than geology.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "fad571a0-0c91-4bf9-a3c7-d1c44193c4ab",
                            "text": "Ask About Booms",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "0302d0fe-5b7c-4e18-94d1-2e95c91f0ca1",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "32",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "541f452f-c749-4bb6-b35e-1b8ef6c81988",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cab04a03-a509-4566-aff5-52fd14a13fa2",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "What happens if nothing goes near the Boom? Is there a way to get back Booms that haven't exploded without blowing yourself up?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "191fa5ca-a14b-473e-b2aa-5705c8e7f9a1",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Of course there is a way to retrieve unexploded Booms! The Headmaster takes a mighty dim view of exploding students in Science lab.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b88b3be8-2033-4f30-beca-f7fe832cbf6f",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "You just have to pull the string on the top to disarm a Boom.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "d5e637b4-9528-45b6-bc28-f7a174b94d97",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky About Booms",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "25a2d4dd-89eb-4a51-9c9f-f993ae0a955d",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "32",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "b58ec564-2002-4076-955b-15ae83ed2032",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "dc64c677-5f69-4e89-a65d-9fae4d831a0a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "So, after you trigger it, if nothing comes near a Boom, is it a bust?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ea5b076d-6552-46ad-8d37-eee293b7662b",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Well, in that situation, it certainly doesn't com-bust.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
